cussing a semi-classical approximation which\nreproduces the entanglement entropy at short to medium time scales and can be\npotentially useful in situations with more complicated geometries where\nclassical simulation methods starts to become inefficient.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Mar 2022 17:00:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-07"}
